Description: This registry defines the messages for Embedded Remote Support.

GenericTransmitError.Description: Generic Transmit Error. Transmission to the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver was unsuccessful.
GenericTransmitError.Resolution: Please check connectivity between Management Processor and the Insight Remote Support receiver.

ClientTransmitTimeout.Description: Client Transmit Timeout. Transmission to the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver was unsuccessful.
ClientTransmitTimeout.Resolution: Please check connectivity between Management Processor and the Insight Remote Support receiver.

ClientReceiveTimeout.Description: Client Receive Timeout. Transmission to the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver was unsuccessful.
ClientReceiveTimeout.Resolution: Please check connectivity between Management Processor and the Insight Remote Support receiver.

TransmitBufferTooShort.Description: Transmit Buffer Too Short. Transmission to the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver was unsuccessful.
TransmitBufferTooShort.Resolution: Please check connectivity between Management Processor and the Insight Remote Support receiver and retry.

InvalidReceiveBuffer.Description: Invalid Receive Buffer. Transmission to the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver was unsuccessful.
InvalidReceiveBuffer.Resolution: Please check connectivity between Management Processor and the Insight Remote Support receiver and retry.

InvalidFileDescriptor.Description: Invalid File Descriptor. Transmission to the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver was unsuccessful.
InvalidFileDescriptor.Resolution: Please check connectivity between Management Processor and the Insight Remote Support receiver and retry.

ReceiveBIOError.Description: Receive BIO Error. Transmission to the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver was unsuccessful.
ReceiveBIOError.Resolution: Please check connectivity between Management Processor and the Insight Remote Support receiver and retry.

ClientReceiveError.Description: Client Receive Error. Transmission to the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver was unsuccessful.
ClientReceiveError.Resolution: Please check connectivity between Management Processor and the Insight Remote Support receiver and retry.

ConnectBIOerror.Description: Connect BIO error. Transmission to the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver was unsuccessful.
ConnectBIOerror.Resolution: Please check connectivity between Management Processor and the Insight Remote Support receiver and retry.

CannotConnectToRemoteHost.Description: Can not connect to remote host. Transmission to the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver was unsuccessful.
CannotConnectToRemoteHost.Message: Can not connect to remote host.
CannotConnectToRemoteHost.Resolution: Please check connectivity between Management Processor and the Insight Remote Support receiver and retry.

InvalidConnectFileDescriptor.Description: Invalid Connect File Descriptor. Transmission to the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver was unsuccessful.

ErrorReadingERSConfiguration.Description: Error reading Embedded Remote Support configuration.
ErrorReadingERSConfiguration.Message: Error reading Embedded Remote Support configuration.

NoActiveHealthFilestoReport.Description: No Active Health Files to Report.
NoActiveHealthFilestoReport.Message: No Active Health Files to Report.

InvalidNumberOfDaysToReport.Description: Invalid Number of Days to Report.
InvalidNumberOfDaysToReport.Message: Invalid Number of Days to Report.

CannotConnectToProxyServer.Description: Unable to connect to the proxy server.
CannotConnectToProxyServer.Message: Unable to connect to the proxy server.
CannotConnectToProxyServer.Resolution: Please verify proxy settings and connectivity.

HttpServerProtocolError.Description: HTTP Server Protocol error occurred while communicating with the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver.
HttpServerProtocolError.Message: HTTP Server Protocol error occurred while communicating with the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver.

NoServerCertificate.Description: Certificate error occurred while communicating with the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver.
NoServerCertificate.Message: Certificate error occurred while communicating with the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver.

CannotEstablishSSLConnection.Description: Protocol error occurred while communicating with the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver.
CannotEstablishSSLConnection.Message: Protocol error occurred while communicating with the HPE Insight Remote Support receiver.

AuthenticationError.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

MissingDeviceIdentifiers.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

CorruptDeviceIdentifiers.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

InsufficientDeviceIdentifierInformation.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

InvalidDeviceIdentifierInformation.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

StaleDeviceIdentifiers.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

MissingGDID.Description: The GDID was found to be missing.
MissingGDID.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

CorruptGDID.Description: The GDID was found to be corrupted.
CorruptGDID.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

MissingRegistrationToken.Description: The registration token was found to be missing.
MissingRegistrationToken.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

CorruptRegistrationToken.Description: The registration token was found to be corrupted.
CorruptRegistrationToken.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

ExpiredRegistrationToken.Description: The registration token was found to be expired.
ExpiredRegistrationToken.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

UnknownDevice.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

MissingRegistrationInformation.Description: The registration information was found to be missing.
MissingRegistrationInformation.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

CorruptRegistrationInformation.Description: The registration information was found to be corrupted.
CorruptRegistrationInformation.Resolution: Please unregister and re-register the device.

InvalidHPEPassportCredentials.Description: Invalid HPE Passport credentials was provided.
InvalidHPEPassportCredentials.Resolution: Please provide valid HPE Passport credentials.

DeviceAlreadyRegistered.Resolution: Please delete the device from Insight Remote Support user interface and retry registration.

DeviceUnregistrationFailed.Description: Unregistration request was not processed successfully by the HPE Remote Support receiver. Remote Support has been disabled locally. No service events or data collections will be sent until this device has been re-registered.
DeviceUnregistrationFailed.Message: Unregistration request was not processed successfully by the HPE Remote Support receiver.

UserIDIsRequiredField.Description: User ID is a required field.
UserIDIsRequiredField.Message: User ID is a required field.

UserMustHaveAnActiveAuthenticatedSession.Description: User must have an active authenticated session.
UserMustHaveAnActiveAuthenticatedSession.Message: User must have an active authenticated session.

MissingSOAPHeader.Resolution: Please retry your last step. If error persists and device is currently registered, unregister and re-register device.

MissingGUID.Resolution: Please retry your last step. If error persists and device is currently registered, unregister and re-register device.

CorruptGUID.Description: The GUID is found to be corrupted.
CorruptGUID.Resolution: Please retry your last step. If error persists and device is currently registered, unregister and re-register device.

MissingDataPackage.Resolution: Please retry your last step. If error persists and device is currently registered, unregister and re-register device.

DataPackageValidationFailed.Resolution: Please retry your last step. If error persists and device is currently registered, unregister and re-register device.

TooManyAttachments.Resolution: Please retry your last step. If error persists and device is currently registered, unregister and re-register device.

MissingAttachments.Resolution: Please retry your last step. If error persists and device is currently registered, unregister and re-register device.

ChangeOrResetHPEPassportPassword.Description: The HPE Passport password must be changed or reset.
ChangeOrResetHPEPassportPassword.Message: The HPE Passport password must be changed or reset.
ChangeOrResetHPEPassportPassword.Resolution: Please attempt to register again after correcting the HPE Passport problem.

ExpiredHPEPassportCredentials.Resolution: Please attempt to register again after correcting the HPE Passport problem.

HPEPassportAccountLockedOut.Description: The HPE Passport account is locked out.
HPEPassportAccountLockedOut.Resolution: Please attempt to register again after correcting the HPE Passport problem.

UnmatchGDIDAndDeviceIdentifiers.Description: GDID and device identifiers do not match.
UnmatchGDIDAndDeviceIdentifiers.Message: GDID and device identifiers do not match.
UnmatchGDIDAndDeviceIdentifiers.Resolution: If error persists and device is not currently registered, unregister and re-register device.

DeviceIsNotRegistered.Description: Device is not registered. Remote Support registration has been disabled locally on this device. No service events or data collections will be sent until this device has been re-registered.

DeviceDeleted.Description: This device has been previously deleted from the Insight Remote Support user interface.
DeviceDeleted.Message: This device has been previously deleted from the Insight Remote Support user interface.

ServiceUnavailableTemporarily.Description: HPE Remote Support receiver is temporarily unavailable.
ServiceUnavailableTemporarily.Message: HPE Remote Support receiver temporarily unavailable.

GeneralReceiverError.Description: General Receiver Error. HPE Remote Support receiver is temporarily unavailable.

RegistrationRequestCouldNotBeQueued.Description: Registration request could not be queued. HPE Remote Support receiver temporarily unavailable.
RegistrationRequestCouldNotBeQueued.Message: Registration request could not be queued.

HPEPassportSystemFailureOccurred.Description: HPE Passport System failure occurred. A problem has been detected in the HPE Passport system.

InvalidHPEPassportUserID.Description: HPE Passport User ID is invalid.
InvalidHPEPassportUserID.Message: HPE Passport User ID is invalid.
InvalidHPEPassportUserID.Resolution: Please retry registration with a valid user ID.

HPEPassportAccountIsLockedOut.Description: HPE Passport account is locked out.
HPEPassportAccountIsLockedOut.Message: HPE Passport account is locked out.
HPEPassportAccountIsLockedOut.Resolution: Please reset your password and retry registration.

HPEPassportUserHasBeenAddedToaGroup.Description: HPE Passport user has been added to a group.
HPEPassportUserHasBeenAddedToaGroup.Message: HPE Passport user has been added to a group.
HPEPassportUserHasBeenAddedToaGroup.Resolution: Please reset your password and retry registration.

UserHasReachedHalfTheMaximumAllowedLogin.Description: User has reached half the maximum allowed login authentication failures.
UserHasReachedHalfTheMaximumAllowedLogin.Message: User has reached half the maximum allowed login authentication failures.
UserHasReachedHalfTheMaximumAllowedLogin.Resolution: Please verify your username and password are correct and retry registration.

HPEPassportPasswordHasExpired.Resolution: Please update your password and retry registration.

HPEPassportUserIdentityElementsMissing.Description: HPE Passport user identity elements missing.
HPEPassportUserIdentityElementsMissing.Message: HPE Passport user identity elements missing.
HPEPassportUserIdentityElementsMissing.Resolution: Please update your HPE Passport profile and retry registration.

HPEPassportSecurityQandAIsNotCompliant.Description: HPE Passport Security Q and A is not compliant.
HPEPassportSecurityQandAIsNotCompliant.Message: HPE Passport Security Q and A is not compliant.
HPEPassportSecurityQandAIsNotCompliant.Resolution: Please update your HPE Passport security Q and A and retry registration.

IncorrectHPEPassportPassword.Resolution: Please retry registration using the correct password.

UserMustEnterAnHPEPassportSecurityQandAa.Description: User must enter an HPE Passport security Q and A and change password.
UserMustEnterAnHPEPassportSecurityQandAa.Message: User must enter an HPE Passport security Q and A and change password.
UserMustEnterAnHPEPassportSecurityQandAa.Resolution: Please update your security Q and A, update your password and retry registration.

InvalidConfigurationForConnectModel.Description: Configuration not supported for current connect model.
InvalidConfigurationForConnectModel.Message: Configuration not supported for current connect model.

Name: Embedded Remote Support Message Registry
